%% MVVM + Use Case flow - User action to state update

sequenceDiagram
    participant V as View (UI)
    participant VM as ViewModel
    participant UC as Use Case
    participant R as Repository (interface)
    participant D as Domain (Entity)

    V->>VM: User action (event)
    VM->>UC: invoke(params)
    UC->>R: getById / save
    R-->>UC: domain model
    UC->>D: business logic (e.g. sale.addLineItem)
    D-->>UC: updated aggregate
    UC->>R: save(aggregate)
    UC-->>VM: Result / Flow
    VM->>VM: update UiState
    VM-->>V: StateFlow / LiveData
    V->>V: Re-compose / update UI
